    "internal.about.eyebrow": "About us",
    "internal.about.title": "Technical expertise meets an intercultural perspective.",
    "internal.about.text": "GSS grows from international experience, social engagement and a consistently practical view of digitalization and professional development.",
    "internal.about.subTitle": "A path with substance.",
    "internal.about.p1": "The founder is a systems and computer engineer. Her degree was recognized in Germany in 2021. She gained experience as an analyst and programmer at Dominican Republic Customs, delivered staff training and led two projects in Hesse with responsibility for planning, organization and implementation.",
    "internal.about.p2": "As an IHK-qualified German-Spanish language mediator, she combines technical, organizational and intercultural expertise. GSS translates this experience into accessible training, coaching and consulting solutions for people and organizations.",
