    "azavPage.eyebrow": "Quality, approval and funding",
    "azavPage.title": "AZAV and funding: developing continuing education responsibly.",
    "azavPage.text": "GSS develops potentially fundable training and coaching services with a clear distinction between the quality path, approval and individual funding decisions.",
    "azavPage.cta": "Discuss funding options",
    "azavPage.legalCta": "View legal information",
    "azavPage.pillarsTitle": "The three requirements",
    "azavPage.pillarsText": "Funding eligibility does not arise from advertising, but from documented approvals and an individual decision by the competent body.",
    "azavPage.providerTitle": "Provider approval",
    "azavPage.providerText": "An accredited competent body assesses the education provider's capability, reliability, professional competence and quality system.",
    "azavPage.measureTitle": "Measure approval",
    "azavPage.measureText": "Each specific fundable training or coaching measure requires approval for its documented scope.",
    "azavPage.decisionTitle": "Funding decision",
    "azavPage.decisionText": "The Agentur für Arbeit or Jobcenter assesses requirements and decides individually. There is no automatic funding guarantee.",
    "azavPage.fundingTitle": "Possible funding routes",
    "azavPage.fundingText": "The appropriate route depends on employment status, objective, measure and consultation with the competent body.",
    "azavPage.qcgTitle": "Employee qualification",
    "azavPage.qcgText": "Under section 82 SGB III, training costs may be covered fully or partly and wage subsidies may be granted. Requirements and amounts depend, among other things, on the measure and company size.",
    "azavPage.voucherTitle": "Bildungsgutschein and AVGS",
    "azavPage.voucherText": "The education voucher and activation and placement voucher are only possible where individual requirements are met and a suitable approved measure exists.",
    "azavPage.moneyTitle": "Qualifizierungsgeld",
    "azavPage.moneyText": "Qualifizierungsgeld may provide wage-replacement support where structural change creates qualification needs. Statutory and company requirements must be met.",
    "azavPage.costsTitle": "Costs and subsidies",
    "azavPage.costsText": "Cost coverage and subsidies vary by individual case. Statements such as “100% funded” will only be used when all requirements have been assessed and confirmed.",
    "azavPage.aiTitle": "AI literacy as a company responsibility",
    "azavPage.aiText": "Article 4 of the EU AI Act requires providers and deployers of AI systems to take measures ensuring a sufficient level of AI literacy among their staff.",
    "azavPage.aiTechTitle": "Technical understanding","azavPage.aiTechText": "Understand functionality, opportunities, limits and data quality.",
    "azavPage.aiLawTitle": "Law and responsibility","azavPage.aiLawText": "Consider privacy, transparency, human oversight, risks and internal rules.",
    "azavPage.aiPracticeTitle": "Practice and transfer","azavPage.aiPracticeText": "Develop use cases, processes and skills appropriate to role, experience and context.",
    "azavPage.processEyebrow": "Process","azavPage.processTitle": "From need to possible funding",
    "azavPage.step1Title": "Clarify the need","azavPage.step1Text": "Target group, skills needs, company situation and desired results are assessed.",
    "azavPage.step2Title": "Check requirements","azavPage.step2Text": "Approval status, funding instrument, competent body and required evidence are reviewed.",
    "azavPage.step3Title": "Application and delivery","azavPage.step3Text": "Funding-related delivery starts only after a positive decision. GSS documents quality, participation and transfer.",
    "azavPage.disclaimer": "Transparency notice: GSS is developing an AZAV-oriented quality structure. This page does not represent an existing provider or measure approval or a funding commitment.",
    "azavPage.entryEyebrow": "Orientation · Offers · Advice",
    "azavPage.entryTitle": "Funding",
    "azavPage.entryText": "Find the right entry point for funding options, the Bildungsgutschein or AVGS process, future funded courses and personal AZAV advice.",
