    "azavPage.audiencesEyebrow": "Who funding may be relevant for",
    "azavPage.audiencesTitle": "Advice aligned with your starting situation.",
    "azavPage.audiencesText": "The responsible Agentur für Arbeit, Jobcenter or Arbeitgeber-Service decides eligibility and scope. GSS supports orientation, offer documents and preparation.",
    "azavPage.audienceJobseekerTitle": "For jobseekers",
    "azavPage.audienceJobseekerText": "A Bildungsgutschein or AVGS may be considered depending on the objective, suitability and labour-market necessity.",
    "azavPage.audienceEmployeeTitle": "For employees",
    "azavPage.audienceEmployeeText": "Training costs and wage subsidies may be funded under certain conditions.",
    "azavPage.audienceCompanyTitle": "For companies",
    "azavPage.audienceCompanyText": "Qualification planning, collective applications and Qualifizierungsgeld require individual coordination with the Arbeitgeber-Service.",
    "azavPage.audienceReturnerTitle": "For returners and career changers",
    "azavPage.audienceReturnerText": "Suitable qualification routes can be assessed after a longer absence or during career reorientation.",
    "azavPage.optionsEyebrow": "Funding options",
    "azavPage.optionsTitle": "Distinguish the instruments before selecting an offer.",
    "azavPage.optionsText": "Not every instrument suits every person or measure. Binding information is provided exclusively by the responsible funding body.",
    "azavPage.optionBgsTitle": "Bildungsgutschein",
    "azavPage.optionBgsText": "For vocational training under section 81 SGB III. Voucher, provider and specific measure must match; the voucher may be limited in time, region and educational objective.",
    "azavPage.optionAvgsTitle": "AVGS for coaching and qualification",
    "azavPage.optionAvgsText": "For activation and occupational integration measures under section 45 SGB III. Objective, duration, validity and region follow from the voucher and approval notice.",
    "azavPage.optionEmployeesTitle": "Employee funding",
    "azavPage.optionEmployeesText": "Employees may receive subsidies for course costs and wages. Many funding routes require more than 120 hours and approved offers.",
    "azavPage.optionQualificationTitle": "Qualifizierungsgeld",
    "azavPage.optionQualificationText": "May replace part of wages where structural change creates qualification needs. Specific company, collective-agreement and measure requirements apply.",
    "azavPage.voucherPathEyebrow": "Your route to a Bildungsgutschein or AVGS",
    "azavPage.voucherPathTitle": "From first orientation to an approved start.",
    "azavPage.voucherStep1Title": "Non-binding orientation with GSS",
    "azavPage.voucherStep1Text": "Objective, starting point, desired qualification and possible routes are clarified in advance. GSS does not issue a funding commitment.",
    "azavPage.voucherStep2Title": "Advice from the responsible body",
    "azavPage.voucherStep2Text": "Agentur für Arbeit, Jobcenter or Arbeitgeber-Service assess need, suitability, necessity and the appropriate instrument.",
    "azavPage.voucherStep3Title": "Match an approved offer",
    "azavPage.voucherStep3Text": "Voucher requirements, educational objective, duration, region, provider and measure approval, and offer documents are checked.",
    "azavPage.voucherStep4Title": "Approval, enrolment and start",
    "azavPage.voucherStep4Text": "Funded participation begins only after written approval and completed enrolment. Participation, quality and results are documented.",
    "azavPage.catalogEyebrow": "Funded courses",
    "azavPage.catalogTitle": "Future access to approved offers.",
    "azavPage.catalogText": "Once approved measures are available, this area will lead to the GSS funding portal on the subdomain. Offers, requirements, dates and approval details will be displayed transparently there.",
    "azavPage.catalogCta": "Open the offer portal",
    "azavPage.catalogDataTitle": "Data for each offer",
    "azavPage.catalogDataText": "Title, target group, educational objective, content, learning format, duration, teaching units, dates, location, entry requirements and completion.",
    "azavPage.catalogApprovalTitle": "Transparent approval",
    "azavPage.catalogApprovalText": "Approval status, field, measure number, competent body, validity and funding instrument are displayed only after documented release.",
    "azavPage.catalogQualityTitle": "Quality and support",
    "azavPage.catalogQualityText": "Teaching staff, learning support, attendance, performance evidence, feedback, complaints route and participation certificate are described.",
    "azavPage.complianceEyebrow": "Quality and auditability",
    "azavPage.complianceTitle": "Prepared for competent bodies, funding bodies and the AMDL inspection service.",
    "azavPage.complianceText": "A professional AZAV structure does not end with the certificate. Processes, delivery and results must remain traceable, current and auditable.",
    "azavPage.complianceQmTitle": "Quality management",
    "azavPage.complianceQmText": "Customer and labour-market orientation, objectives, internal audits, indicators, management review, improvement and complaints management.",
    "azavPage.compliancePeopleTitle": "People and roles",
    "azavPage.compliancePeopleText": "Evidence for management, teaching and specialist staff, qualifications, experience, training, cover, responsibilities and privacy.",
    "azavPage.complianceMeasureTitle": "Measure design",
    "azavPage.complianceMeasureText": "Target group, objective, content, methods, duration, costs, labour-market relevance, individual support and expected success.",
    "azavPage.complianceDeliveryTitle": "Delivery and documentation",
    "azavPage.complianceDeliveryText": "Contracts, participant files, attendance, progress, deviations, privacy, evaluation, integration support and completion evidence.",
    "azavPage.complianceCooperationTitle": "Cooperation and reporting",
    "azavPage.complianceCooperationText": "Structured communication with competent bodies, Agentur für Arbeit, Jobcenter, Arbeitgeber-Service, KURSNET or mein NOW and partners.",
    "azavPage.complianceAuditTitle": "Audit readiness",
    "azavPage.complianceAuditText": "Current certificates, site and field evidence, change management and complete records for on-site and remote inspections.",
    "azavPage.complianceNote": "Binding notice: certificate or measure numbers, fields and validity dates may only be published once the corresponding evidence exists.",
